565
01:01:22.054 --> 01:01:24.473
"Dear Jack..."
That's me!

566
01:01:24.848 --> 01:01:27.558
"My name is Ohm Bauman."

567
01:01:27.559 --> 01:01:28.894
Ohm? Okay.

568
01:01:29.645 --> 01:01:33.774
"I am ten years old
and my mom died last year."

569
