616
01:15:59.472 --> 01:16:02.516
Mr Cob sent me out here
to look for the key.

617
01:16:02.517 --> 01:16:04.101
and when I got here.
the gate was unlocked.

618
01:16:04.102 --> 01:16:05.895
so I went up.
- And?

619
01:16:06.980 --> 01:16:09.190
