- What?

621
01:16:12.318 --> 01:16:15.320
- Where is he?
- He's on his way to the airport.

622
01:16:15.321 --> 01:16:17.948
Well. he was too drunk to drive.
so I took him down to town.

623
01:16:17.949 --> 01:16:19.909
